<h1>Christmas beauty.</h1>  
<p>Because yesterday we’ve spent almost the entire day in the car, today we went for a walk first thing in the morning. It’s a wonderful morning - proper Christmas morning - the snow is falling and there are a lot of Christmas lights around. Even in-city walking today is gorgeous!</p>
